Description_en: The concept FEMALE is used for representing the human sexes in the context of interchange of information in the social sciences domain.
Description_es: Uno de los sexos humanos en el contexto del intercambio de información en el dominio de las ciencias sociales.
Description_sl: Koncept Ženska se uporablja za zastopanje človeških spolov v okviru izmenjave informacij na področju socialne vede.

Description_fr: Le concept femelle est utilisé pour représenter les sexes humains dans le contexte de l'échange d'informations dans le domaine des sciences sociales.

Description_en: The concept MALE is used for representing the human sexes in the context of interchange of information in the social sciences domain.

Description_en: The concept NOT APPLICABLE is used in the context of interchange of information in the social sciences domain when none of the sexes can be represented.
Description_es: No aplica se utiliza en el contexto del intercambio de información en el dominio de las ciencias sociales cuando no se pueden representar ninguno de los sexos.

Description_en: The concept NOT KNOWN is used in the context of interchange of information in the social sciences domain when the human sex is unkown.

Description_en: The concept NOT STATED is used in the context of interchange of information in the social sciences domain when the human sex is not stated.
